{"type": "article", "id": 10559, "title": "Peel壁灯", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-09T07:16:51Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235750l1UOj5I2VpFbCiG7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<span>YOY 设计事务所的设计师再一次利用视觉差来设计壁灯，看起来就像剥开了墙皮才透过隔壁家的灯光。十分有趣，且第一次见的人一定会好奇当中原理。其实是一个纸飞机形状的灯，通过钩子固定在墙角，营造出一种墙皮被剥开的感觉。亮光使用有机发光二极管，能达到最细微的光线效果。</span><a href=\"http://yoy-idea.jp/works/peel/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里查看官网信息</a><span>。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235749yNPu8zxLK4GBgJXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5953125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235750bZ27itHwUg4MqvBp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}